portal.loadingProviderInfo: Reading available Social Media Provider. Please wait ...
portal.registeredFillOut:
Congratulations!

Your Logon via Social Provider <%= providerFullName %> was successful.
Now you have to finish your Registration for iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal!

Please fillout the follow form with your contact and company data.
Send the form by pressing Complete Registration button.
After finishing the request you have to wait until access is granted by your responsible clerk.
portal.registeredSuccessful:
Congratulations!

You are now registered for the iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal.

Before you can use the portal, your responsible Clerk will have to confirm your application.
If there is anything missing or wrong, they will contact you via mail or phone.

Once registration has been completed, you will receive an email. Then, you can start working with the iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal.
portal.registrationFailed:
Oops!

Your registration to iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal failed!

Following issue occurred while registering.
Code: <%= resultcode %>  Message:
<%= resultmsg %>
portal.standardGreeting:
Hello!

This is the iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal.
If you want to use this portal you first have to register via a Social Media Provider from the list below.
Please first signon with the Social Media Provider.

After successful Logon, you will be redirected to the iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal.
and you can continue the registration.

Good Luck!
portal.invitationGreeting:
Hello!

You're invited as a new Bidder into the iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal.

Are you <%=fullname%>
and are you the owner of the following email adresse
<%=email%>

If so you are allowed to continue with the registration to the Portal.
Please login via your Social Media Provider from the list below.


After successful Logon, you will be redirected to the iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal.
and you can confirm the registration.

Good Luck!
portal.invitationFailed:
Oops!

Your invitation to iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal failed!

Following issue occurred while registering.
Code: <%= resultcode %>  Message:
<%= resultmsg %>

Sorry for the inconvenience!
We can not continued.
Please contact your responsible helpdesk for further support.
portal.finishedinfo: Receive an email after inivitation finished?
portal.invitationFillout:
Congratulations!

Your Logon via Social Provider <%= providerFullName %> was successful.
Now you have to finish your Invitation for iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal!

Please fillout the follow form with your contact and company data.
Send the form by pressing Complete Invitation Now button.
After finishing the request you have to wait until access is granted by your responsible clerk.
portal.invitationComplete:
Congratulations! Your Logon via Social Provider <%= providerFullName %> was successful.
Now you have to finish your Invitation for iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal!

Please verify your data and fillout the missing form data. After finishing the last step of the invitagtion you will get a url. Please save this url for later access the iTWO4.0 Portal.
portal.invitationSuccessful:
Congratulations!

You are now registered for the iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal.

You can now navigate back with the Button Back to Logon to the Logon Page and start working with the iTWO 4.0 Internet Portal.
